&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We offer you the opportunity to join the leading Spanish company in the IT sector, with more than 25 years of experience and one of the most solid track records as a provider of technological solutions for companies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a growing company with more than 400 employees and offices in Logroño, Madrid, Barcelona, Seville, Bilbao and Valencia.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Since August 2013, we have been part of the IONOS Group, Europe&#39;s leading digitalisation partner for small and medium-sized companies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In short, we are a multicultural team that’s passionate about technology, bringing our professional experience from over a dozen countries: Germany, Argentina, Spain, the United States, France, the Philippines, Italy, Poland, Portugal, the United Kingdom, Romania...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;IONOS, the leading European provider of cloud infrastructure, cloud services, and hosting services, stands for open structures, a vibrant work culture, and flat hierarchies with a dynamic team spirit. We firmly believe that work can also be fun and offer the right environment for it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an outstanding, results-oriented Commercial General Manager to drivestrategic direction and business development. The role will involve:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leading and managing the entire business operations with a strong focus on marketing and sales within a global, functional organizational structure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Developing, implementing, and monitoring long-term growth strategies to achieve company goals.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implementing and monitoring technology, go-to-market and marketing &amp;amp; sales strategy to ensure that IONOS remains at the forefront of its industry.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitoring and analyzing market and industry trends to identify opportunities and mitigate risks.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In terms of functional and operational management, the responsibilities will include:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead local marketing and sales strategy and execution, from branding, customer acquisition to retention, cross- and upselling as well as win-back.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead all localization efforts to best tailor the go-to-market approach to local requirements and local customer needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide clear feedback on local business priorities and opportunities to the headquarters to inform about strategic roadmap and investment discussions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Closely and seamlessly collaborate with the central teams and functions of the IONOS Group to leverage best practices and central resources from the group and further develop the local brand.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate and prioritize projects and initiatives in collaboration with the relevant departments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and foster internal synergies within the IONOS Group.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Increase operational efficiency and performance by optimizing internal processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the realm of team leadership and employee development, the new manager will be entrusted with the following responsibilities:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leading and inspiring a talented and diverse interdisciplinary team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building and leading a high-performing sales and marketing team to drive company growth and strengthen the market position.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hiring, training, developing and coaching a high-performing team through effective leadership practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cultivating a work environment that fosters innovation, collaboration, and continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establishing and maintaining strong relationships with key stakeholders, including customers, partners, communities and regulators as well as govern

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We offer you the opportunity to join the leading Spanish company in the IT sector, with more than 25 years of experience and one of the most solid track records as a provider of technological solutions for companies.&lt;/p&gt;
