&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;9,1,0&quot;&gt;Take Technical Command: Become the subject matter expert for Linux platforms, Ceph storage, and OpenStack.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;9,2,0&quot;&gt;Mitigate Risks: Ensure that the Telekom migration and the stability of the &lt;em data-path-to-node=&quot;9,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;75&quot;&gt;Stretch&lt;/em&gt; platform are not compromised during the transition.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;9,3,0&quot;&gt;Design the Future: Establish on-call policies, operational workflows, and Infrastructure as Code (IaC) automation standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;What we&#39;d like to see&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;11&quot;&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;11&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;21&quot;&gt;&quot;Player-Coach&quot;&lt;/strong&gt; who commands the respect of engineers because you have been in the trenches yourself.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;12,0,0&quot;&gt;Credible Leadership: 2+ years managing technical teams and the ability to attract top-tier talent within the Spanish market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;12,1,0&quot;&gt;Solid Technical Foundation: 5+ years of real-world experience in large-scale Linux systems administration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;12,2,0&quot;&gt;Cloud &amp;amp; Storage Expert: Essential hands-on experience with Ceph and OpenStack.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;12,3,0&quot;&gt;Automation Master: Proficiency in Ansible, Puppet, or Terraform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;12,4,0&quot;&gt;Solution-Oriented Mindset: The ability to transform chaos into scalable, well-documented systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Expectations&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Being part of a multidisciplinary team passionate about technology, with an open and dynamic culture, where experimentation and discussion are encouraged to progress at work, always with respect and inclusion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We offer personalised career plans, annual performance evaluations and programmes to develop skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We operate in Spanish and English and therefore provide unlimited language training. We work on international projects and define best practices with United Internet partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We have flexible start and finish times, respecting a schedule of meetings in the central part of the morning and a range of work from 7 a.m. to 9 p.m. with a hybrid model in one of our offices (Alcobendas, Valencia, Barcelona, Seville or Logroño).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
