&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;9,3,0&quot;&gt;Knowledge Transfer: Collaborate with colleagues in Cologne (Germany) to absorb institutional knowledge of legacy systems and document critical processes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;9,4,0&quot;&gt;Continuous Improvement: Identify performance bottlenecks and propose/implement proactive improvements to the existing architecture.&lt;/p&gt;
